trans-unit.source: Defines common user interface (UI) properties used by ASP.NET <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Definerer vanlige bruker brukergrensesnittet (UI) egenskaper som brukes av ASP.NET <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The IWebPart interface provides several UI-oriented properties that enhance the user experience of working with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IWebPart inneholder flere UI-orientert egenskaper som forbedrer brukeropplevelsen av arbeid med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: When you create controls that derive from the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, you get an implementation of all the properties in the IWebPart interface, because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> base class implements this interface.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter Kontroller avledes fra grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen du får en implementering av alle egenskapene i grensesnittet IWebPart fordi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>basisklassen implementerer dette grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: You can use existing user controls, ASP.NET controls, or custom server controls that do not inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class as part of a Web Parts application, and they can also use these UI-oriented properties declared by the IWebPart interface.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke eksisterende brukerkontroller, ASP.NET-kontroller eller egendefinerte serverkontroller ikke arver fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen som en del av en webdeler-programmet, og de kan også bruke egenskapene UI-orientert deklarert av grensesnittet IWebPart.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If you place existing server controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zone, at run time they are wrapped with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter eksisterende serverkontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>sone, på kjøretidspunktet de står i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> class inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> base class, it enables existing server controls to act as true <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls and it adds to them the properties of the IWebPart interface.
trans-unit.target: Fordi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>klassen arver fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>basisklassen, gjør det mulig for eksisterende serverkontroller kan brukes som true <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, og legger til dem egenskaper for grensesnittet IWebPart.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>

trans-unit.source: If you place server controls that are not <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls in zones, they can use the IWebPart properties at run time, and you can also declare values for those properties on server controls in the markup of the page (in page persistence format).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter serverkontroller ikke <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller i soner, kan de bruke egenskapene IWebPart ved kjøretid, og du kan også angi verdier for disse egenskapene på serverkontroller i markup på siden (i siden utholdenhet format).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: However, because these properties are only available to the server controls at run time, design-time coding features such as IntelliSense do not recognize IWebPart properties that are declared on server controls.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid fordi disse egenskapene er bare tilgjengelig for serverkontroller ved kjøretid, gjenkjenner utformingen kunnskap funksjoner som IntelliSense ikke IWebPart egenskaper som er deklarert på serverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: Declared properties on these controls still work when you load the page, but Microsoft Visual Studio does not recognize the properties as valid at design time.
trans-unit.target: Deklarerte egenskaper på disse kontrollene fremdeles fungere når du laster inn siden, men Microsoft Visual Studio gjenkjenner ikke egenskapene som gyldig under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: If you want to add the IWebPart properties to existing server and user controls to enhance the design-time user experience, you can implement the IWebPart interface in a server control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til egenskapene IWebPart eksisterende server og brukerkontroller å forbedre utformingen brukeropplevelsen, kan du kan implementere grensesnittet IWebPart i en serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: Perhaps the main reason to implement the IWebPart interface is for controls that do not support the use of expando (custom) properties.
trans-unit.target: Hovedgrunnen til å implementere grensesnittet IWebPart er kanskje for kolonner som ikke støtter bruk av expando (egendefinert) egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: Expando properties are strings that can be added to a class dynamically as a property, by means of the <xref:System.Web.UI.IAttributeAccessor> interface.
trans-unit.target: Expando er strenger som kan legges til en klasse dynamisk som en egenskap ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.IAttributeAccessor>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.IAttributeAccessor>

trans-unit.source: Controls that implement this interface, including the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> class and its children, can use expando properties.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som implementerer dette grensesnittet inkludert i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>klassen og de underordnede objektene, kan bruke expando egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, all ASP.NET server controls, custom controls that derive from them, Web user controls, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls support the use of expando properties.
trans-unit.target: Derfor alle serverkontroller for ASP.NET, egendefinerte kontroller som avledet fra disse webkontroller for brukeren, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller støtter bruk av expando egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: But custom controls that inherit directly from the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> class do not support expando properties.
trans-unit.target: Men egendefinerte kontroller som arver direkte fra grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>klassen støtter ikke expando egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control>

trans-unit.source: Thus, if you declare these controls within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>, you will not be able to declare the common IWebPart properties on the controls, properties such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Description%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Derfor Hvis du deklarerer disse kontrollene i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>du vil ikke deklarere vanlige IWebPart med egenskapene i kontrollene egenskaper som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Description%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Description%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: If you want to use these properties with such controls, you must implement the IWebPart interface.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil bruke disse egenskapene med slike kontroller, må du implementere grensesnittet IWebPart.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL to an image that represents a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adressen til et bilde som representerer en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen i en katalog for kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Web Parts applications often provide a catalog (or list) of controls that users can add to a page.
trans-unit.target: Deler webprogrammer inneholder ofte en katalog (eller liste) av kontroller som brukere kan legge til en side.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogIconImageUrl property on a control contains the URL to an image that represents the control when it appears in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogIconImageUrl i en kontroll inneholder URL-adressen til et bilde som representerer kontrollen når det blir vist i en katalog.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the URL to an image used to represent the control in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer URL-adressen til et bilde som brukes til å representere kontrollen i en katalog.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a brief phrase that summarizes what a control does, for use in ToolTips and catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et kort uttrykk som summerer hva en kontroll har, for bruk i verktøytips og kataloger for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The Description property value is typically used as a descriptive string for a control in catalogs that provide lists of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, and as a ToolTip in a control's title bar.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien beskrivelse brukes vanligvis som en beskrivende streng for en kontroll i kataloger som gir lister over <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, og som et verktøytips i feltet for tittel. en kontroll</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The content of the property appears in a ToolTip when a user positions the mouse pointer over the title text in a control's title bar.
trans-unit.target: Innholdet i egenskapen vises i et verktøytips når en bruker plasserer pekeren over tittelteksten i tittellinjen for en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A string that briefly summarizes the control's functionality.
trans-unit.target: En streng som kort oppsummerer kontrollens funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets a string that is concatenated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title*> property value to form a complete title for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en streng som er slått sammen med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title*>egenskapsverdien å lage en fullstendig tittel for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title*>

trans-unit.source: The Subtitle property is used to return a default subtitle string for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is appended to the control's title in the title bar.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen undertittel brukes til å returnere en standard undertittel streng for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll som legges til kontrollens tittel i Tittel-feltet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If you provide a default value for the Subtitle property in a control that implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart> interface, the Web Parts control set automatically appends it to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A> property of the control at run time.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir en standardverdi for egenskapen undertittel i en kontroll som implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart>grensesnitt webdeler kontrollen automatisk tilføyer dem til verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A>kontrollen ved kjøretid.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Title%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart>

trans-unit.source: A string that serves as a subtitle for the control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som fungerer som en Undertittel for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the title of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tittelen på en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The visible title text in a control's title bar is set by the Title property.
trans-unit.target: Synlig tittelteksten i tittellinjen for en kontroll er angitt av egenskapen tittel.

trans-unit.source: If you do not supply a title for a control, the Web Parts control set automatically calculates a default string to use as a title.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en tittel for en kontroll, beregner webdeler kontrollen automatisk en standardstrengen som skal brukes som en tittel.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Also, it is possible to provide a default subtitle that is appended to the title string.
trans-unit.target: Det er også mulig å angi en standard undertittel som skal legges til en tittel-streng.

trans-unit.source: For details, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Subtitle%2A>.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Subtitle%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.Subtitle%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the title of the control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder tittelen på kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL to an image used to represent a Web Parts control in the control's own title bar.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adressen til et bilde som brukes til å representere en webdeler kontroll i tittellinjen kontrollens egen.

trans-unit.source: The TitleIconImageUrl property provides a way to associate an icon with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TitleIconImageUrl gjør det mulig å knytte et ikon med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The icon appears in the control's own title bar.
trans-unit.target: Ikonet vises i tittellinjen kontrollens egen.

trans-unit.source: For thematic consistency, application developers might want to make this icon similar to the image that represents the control in a catalog of Web Parts controls (the image referenced in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A> property).
trans-unit.target: For thematic konsekvens utviklere programmer vil gjøre dette ikonet ligner på bildet som representerer kontrollen i en katalog med webdeler kontroller (bildet det refereres til i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>egenskapen).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: As it is implemented in the Web Parts control set, the TitleIconImageUrl property can be personalized by end users to change the image or icon that appears in a control's title bar.
trans-unit.target: Fordi den er implementert i kontrollen webdeler angitt TitleIconImageUrl egenskapen kan tilpasses etter sluttbrukerne mulighet til å endre bildet eller ikonet som vises i tittellinjen for en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the URL to an image.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer URL-adressen til et bilde.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a URL to supplemental information about a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en URL-adresse til tilleggsinformasjon en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: When you assign a URL to the TitleUrl property, the title of the control becomes a link.
trans-unit.target: Når du tilordner en URL-adresse til egenskapen TitleUrl, blir tittelen på kontrollen en kobling.

trans-unit.source: The purpose of this property is to provide a convenient way for end users to access additional information about a control.
trans-unit.target: Formålet for denne egenskapen er å angi enkelt for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å få tilgang til mer informasjon om en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The additional information could provide copyright data, contact data, details about the creator of the control, or a summary of the control's purpose.
trans-unit.target: Mer informasjon kan angi om dataene, kontakt data, detaljer om oppretteren av kontrollen eller et sammendrag av kontrollens formålet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Normally, you would not use the TitleUrl property to link to Help content.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Vanligvis du ikke vil bruke egenskapen TitleUrl for å koble til Hjelp-innhold.

trans-unit.source: The best way to provide a link to Help for a control is to use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HelpUrl%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den beste måten å angi en kobling til hjelp for en kontroll er å bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HelpUrl%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HelpUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string that represents a URL to more information about a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer en URL-adresse til mer informasjon om en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").
